          <text><![CDATA[<p> Creating Crop Insurance Certainty for Farmers Act - Amends the Federal Crop Insurance Act to direct the Secretary of Agriculture (USDA) to provide specified advanced public notice and a period for public comment before any modification to the terms or conditions of a crop insurance policy or plan may be made.</p> <p>Authorizes the Secretary to waive such provision in an emergency situation.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
